our motion to overturn,

774
00:48:23,905 --> 00:48:26,403
but right now, no.

775
00:48:26,405 --> 00:48:28,611
I don't think so.

776
00:48:28,613 --> 00:48:31,655
You all right goin' up
against your old boss?

